{"tid":2263023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者放蛇證上水藥房走私仍活躍 代客經澳門珠海寄回大陸 前水貨客自白：3日賺2千，試過滯留大陸瞓桑拿浴","createTime":"2020-10-29T14:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T14:39:14.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"48833bb6796baa97aaccf8c33edcf60b152b0e16","tid":2263023,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:17:27.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n上水石湖墟成為「水貨城」多年，而在疫情之下，不少水貨店藥妝店相繼結業，石湖墟回歸平靜，北區人都說光復上水指日可待。然而記者放蛇後，證實走私活動仍活躍；亦邀請曾經走水貨的大學生分享了看法。有機會興建大型購物城的梧桐河，又將會面臨甚麼問題？<br />\n「我希望大家重拾對自己生活地方的自豪，不介意跟別人說『我是北區人』。」這是《來生不做北區人？》專題中，一位受訪者說的話，也為這個題目下了註腳。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cU0X1flvt6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcU0X1flvt6k&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KL2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=2bf60f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cU0X1flvt6k</a>"},{"pid":"e09fd77e31937d74b8eea4a8071f1bf97217c608","tid":2263023,"uid":347497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"我都唔明有乜好放蛇？人地走水貨得黎又冇擾民。"},{"pid":"e0f45f1436164a6bb4a78b43196212810f1453ec","tid":2263023,"uid":2450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e09fd77e31937d74b8eea4a8071f1bf97217c608","tid":2263023,"uid":347497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"我都唔明有乜好放蛇？人地走水貨得黎又冇擾民。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人做犯法野3日賺2千冇人拉"},{"pid":"a205a1e8c3c2b26f3885da71c1c23e6201fae361","tid":2263023,"uid":67065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e0f45f1436164a6bb4a78b43196212810f1453ec","tid":2263023,"uid":2450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e09fd77e31937d74b8eea4a8071f1bf97217c608","tid":2263023,"uid":347497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:27:01.000Z","msg":"我都唔明有乜好放蛇？人地走水貨得黎又冇擾民。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"唔抵得人做犯法野3日賺2千冇人拉"},"citedBy":0,